name: UmbraMix
description:
UmbraMix

What's UmbraMix?

  • UmbraMix models provide cutting edge epic quality by merging some of the top tier models together for amazing results !

  • UmbraMix shines at generating objects/faces at close range.

Usage

  • For even more epic results, consider using the Hires. fix and/or high sampling step (~40 to ~80) specially when generating high resolution images.

  • Experiment, experiment, experiment!

    • No model is perfect, you may need to experiment and generate multiple images in order to get what you're looking for

    • Using different VAEs to best suit your style is recommended!

    • Extensive usage of ControlNet is recommended!

License

  • Since the models provided here are merges between other models, every model version inherits the license from the respective models that made up the merge
